OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,FThe boss of the Co-op Live has said
OL,7,Fthe venue would love to host the Brits
OL,8,F"for years to come" a week after the
OL,9,Fmajor awards ceremony was held at the
OL,10,Fvenue.
OL,12,FIt comes after a significant week for
OL,13,Fthe 23,500-capacity venue, which also
OL,14,Fhosted a Harry Styles album launch
OL,15,Fshow on Friday, 6 March.
OL,17,FGreg Dunstan, managing director of Co-
OL,18,Fop Live, said Styles's show was a
OL,19,F"massive coup for us" and said
OL,20,F"demonstrates that we are now at the
OL,21,Fforefront of the industry".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@SO]{D@AOU{D@UO]|D@AOU}D@ZO]
