OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,FThe former One Direction member played
OL,7,Fthe Manchester venue to mark the
OL,8,Flaunch of his latest album, Kiss All
OL,9,Fthe Time. Disco, Occasionally.
OL,11,FThe gig, priced at #20 a ticket, was
OL,12,Ffilmed by Netflix and released on the
OL,13,Fstreaming platform on Sunday, 8 March.
OL,15,FIt came days after Styles opened the
OL,16,FBrit Awards at the venue.
OL,18,FCo-op Live hosted the event as part of
OL,19,Fa two-year contract which will also
OL,20,Fsee it stage the 50th anniversary show
OL,21,Fnext year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
