OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,F"It was one of the biggest events
OL,7,Fwe've worked on and it was an amazing
OL,8,Fexperience," Mr Dunstan said. "We
OL,9,Fwould love to stage the Brits for
OL,10,Fyears to come and think we really
OL,11,Fdemonstrated what we can deliver.
OL,13,F"But for now we are focusing on
OL,14,Fhosting again in 2027 and it will be
OL,15,Fanother opportunity to deliver a
OL,16,Ffantastic show."
OL,18,FHe said the Brit Awards and Harry
OL,19,FStyles' "One Night Only" show
OL,20,Fhighlighted the demand for major
OL,21,Fconcerts and events outside London.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@LO]pD@_OUuD@AOUxD@PO]
