OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,FThe boss said: "Since 2024 we have
OL,7,Fstaged a number of exclusive events
OL,8,Fand one-off shows, and will continue
OL,9,Fdoing so.
OL,11,F"It shows the North doesn't have miss
OL,12,Fout on that. We were the only indoor
OL,13,Fvenue Bruce Springsteen played in the
OL,14,FUK, similar with Morrissey's latest
OL,15,Fshows."
OL,17,FThe shows came almost two years after
OL,18,Fthe opening of the venue, which was
OL,19,Fmarred by early technical issues.
OL,26,@nD@POUsD@AOUwD@GO]
