OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,FIn April 2024, capacity was reduced
OL,7,Ffor its first test event with Rick
OL,8,FAstley, while Peter Kay had to
OL,9,Fpostpone his first dates at the venue.
OL,11,FFurther concerts, such as Olivia
OL,12,FRodrigo, were also pushed back due to
OL,13,Fissues, which included a component of
OL,14,Fits heating, ventilation and air
OL,15,Fconditioning system separating and
OL,16,Ffalling.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
