OL,3,C'We'd love to host Brit Awards for
OL,4,Cyears', says Co-op Live boss
OL,6,FMr Dunstan said: "I joined about five
OL,7,Fmonths after opening. I realised quite
OL,8,Fquickly that we had an amazing venue
OL,9,Fand having gone on that journey, the
OL,10,Fteam had showed an unreal resilience.
OL,12,F"Having gone through that, they showed
OL,13,Fa commitment that has allowed us to go
OL,14,Ffrom strength to strength."
OL,16,FListen to the ITV News' entertainment
OL,17,Fpodcast, Unscripted.
